1. PLANNING :
planning -> define project scope -> set obj and goals -> resource planning

2. DEFINE REQ :
define -> functional req -> technical req -> req review and approved

3. DESIGN ARCH :
design -> lld -> hld

4. DEVELOPMENT :
development -> coding std -> scalable code -> version control -> code review

5. TESTING & INTEGRATION :
system testing -> manual -> automation

6. DEPLOYMENT & MONITORING :
release planning -> deployment automation -> maintenance -> feedback -> rollback strategies
